#define ANIMESH_STRENGTH 10000
#define STAND "Watch"
#define LAND "Crouch"
#define WALK "Cool"
#define GREETINGS ["%s, your weakness is an insult to the potential of your species.", "I see nothing here but wasted space, %s.", "Do not bother exerting yourself, %s. You are fundamentally incapable.", "You exist only because I allow it, %s. Remember that.", "Total inefficiency. You are a burden to this gym, %s.", "You are improving, %s, but you remain pitifully primitive.", "A slight increase in output, but it matters little in the grand scheme, %s.", "Don't mistake this incremental movement for true strength, %s.", "You are striving for adequacy, %s. Keep laboring.", "Your struggles are amusing, %s. Nothing more.", "You show a glimmer of utility, %s. Do not falter now.", "Finally, a sign that you might be worth observing, %s.", "Your commitment to discipline is... acceptable, %s.", "You are moving past the herd, %s. Try to maintain the pace.", "Decent effort, %s. But do not believe you have reached your peak.", "You have ambition, %s. That is the first requirement of a warrior.", "I see you pushing your limits, %s. That is the Viltrumite way.", "Your strength is finally beginning to justify your presence, %s.", "You are becoming a useful asset to this facility, %s.", "Keep refining your craft, %s. Excellence is the only standard.", "You have surpassed the majority of your peers, %s.", "A rare display of power, %s. I am actually impressed.", "You demonstrate the focus required for true dominion, %s.", "Efficiency, strength, and resolve—you possess them all, %s.", "You are reaching your potential, %s. Do not stop now.", "You are nearly a god among insects, %s. A remarkable trajectory.", "It is rare to see such power in a lesser species, %s.", "Your strength rivals the finest soldiers, %s. Acknowledge your might.", "An anomaly in this facility, %s. You stand quite apart from the weak.", "You are a weapon, %s. Use that power effectively.", "At last, someone who understands the necessity of strength, %s.", "You are capable of leading your kind, %s. True dominance.", "I recognize your power, %s. It is significant, even to me.", "You have conquered your own limitations, %s. Truly glorious.", "You are a force to be feared, %s. We are not so different."]

#define WrestleWin ["Do you understand now, %s? You are an insect trying to stop a hurricane.","I don't have time for this, %s. Go back to your trivial life before I make it end.","You have strength, I suppose. But it is meaningless against a Viltrumite.","I expected more. You are not worth the air you're breathing, %s.","Do not seek me out again, %s. Next time, I will not be so merciful.","You fight with spirit, %s. It’s almost charming. Now stay down.","I have conquered worlds that would make your civilization look like a sandbox, %s.","You think you’re a hero? You’re just a temporary obstacle.","I’ve had dust mites offer more resistance than that, %s.","You should have stayed out of my way. That was your first and last mistake.","You are stronger than you look, %s. But still, you are nothing to me.","It takes more than grit to survive, %s. It takes power you’ll never possess.","I’m almost disappointed. I wanted to see if you had potential. You don't.","Stay down, %s. You've done your part—which was to fail.","The world is fragile, %s. And you just proved you aren't strong enough to protect it.","You’ve got a backbone, I’ll give you that, %s. Pity it has to be broken.","You’ve done well, %s. For a human. But the result remains the same.","I’m not trying to hurt you, %s. I’m just trying to make you stop.","You forced me to expend energy. That is your only accomplishment today.","Go home, %s. Learn from this. If you survive, you’ll be stronger for it.","That was... actually impressive, %s. You’re the first one to make me blink.","I can see the fire in you. It’s a shame it’s going to be extinguished, %s.","You have power, %s. Why do you waste it on protecting the weak?","You pushed me back. That’s more than most. Don't let it go to your head.","I respect your tenacity, %s. But do not confuse respect with victory.","Finally. A real challenge. You’re a warrior, %s. I haven't enjoyed a fight like this in centuries.","You have the power to rule, %s. Why do you choose to serve these fragile people?","You’re dangerous, %s. I might actually have to take you seriously.","I didn't expect to work this hard today, %s. You’ve earned a swift death.","We are alike, %s. Just imagine what we could do if you chose to see the truth.","At last! A combatant who can actually stand against me. I am... relieved, %s.","You are powerful, %s. You’re the closest thing I’ve seen to a Viltrumite in years.","I’m glad I found you, %s. The galaxy is a lonely place for a god.","You forced me to use my full strength. That is an honor I rarely grant.","You are a legend, %s. It was a privilege to fight someone of your caliber—even if I had to end you."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["A fluke! Do not think this means anything, %s!","I’m leaving, %s. This world is not worth the damage I’d have to cause to win.","I was distracted. Don't think for a second you've bested me, %s.","You’re lucky I’m not in a mood to slaughter today, %s.","This is just a setback. I’ll be back, and I’ll break you.","You got a lucky hit, %s. It won't happen twice.","My armor was compromised... that’s the only reason you’re still standing, %s.","I’m not losing. I’m just withdrawing to plan a better conquest.","Enjoy this moment, %s. It's the only one you'll get.","I have no time for you right now, %s. Consider yourself spared.","You're more capable than you look, %s. I’ll keep that in mind.","You caught me off guard, %s. A mistake I’ll rectify.","You’re holding your own, %s. But you're still not a Viltrumite.","I’ve got better things to do than scrap with you, %s.","Fine. You won the round, %s. Don't act like you've won the war.","You’re annoying, %s. That’s a trait that usually gets people killed.","I'm leaving, %s. Not because I lost, but because this is boring.","You managed to best me, %s. I’m annoyed, but I respect the effort.","You've got potential, %s. Maybe I'll come back and recruit you—or kill you.","Fine, you’ve won. Now get out of my sight before I change my mind.","I’m irritated that you won, %s. I’m going to go recalibrate.","You’re tough, %s. And that’s a dangerous thing to be.","That’s the most interesting fight I’ve had in ages, %s. You earned it, but I hated it.","You know how to push my buttons, %s. Keep it up and see what happens.","You're a powerhouse, %s. I hate to admit it, but you bested me.","Great. Now I’m gonna be angry all day thanks to you, %s.","You got the better of me, %s. Don't think I’m happy about it.","You’re a real heavy hitter, %s. I hate that I had to lose to ya.","I respect ya, %s, but you're still a pain.","That was some serious scrap, %s. Now leave me to my thoughts.","I’m a conqueror, but you're a bigger threat than I realized, %s. You win this round.","It was an honor to go toe-to-toe with ya, but I'm still livid, %s.","You pushed me way past my limits, %s. I haven't felt this frustrated in centuries.","You’re elite, %s. Doesn't mean I gotta like ya.","You've got grit, heart, and power—you’re the real deal, %s. Now get lost before I kill you."]
